title: Alert State Machine

classes: {
  state: {
    style.fill: "#1a1a2e"
    style.stroke: "#3fb950"
    style.font-color: "#e6edf3"
    style.bold: true
  }
  initial_state: {
    style.fill: "#3fb950"
    style.stroke: "#3fb950"
    style.font-color: "#1a1a2e"
    style.bold: true
  }
  transition: {
    style.stroke: "#8b949e"
    style.font-color: "#e6edf3"
  }
}

init: {
  shape: circle
  class: initial_state
  label: ""
}

inactive: Inactive {
  shape: circle
  class: state
}

pending: Pending {
  shape: circle
  class: state
}

firing: Firing {
  shape: circle
  class: state
}

resolved: Resolved {
  shape: circle
  style.fill: "#1a1a2e"
  style.stroke: "#3fb950"
  style.font-color: "#e6edf3"
  style.double-border: true
  style.bold: true
}

init -> inactive: System Start {
  class: transition
}

inactive -> pending: Threshold Exceeded\n& Evaluation Started {
  class: transition
}

pending -> firing: Condition Persists\n& Grace Period Elapsed {
  class: transition
}

pending -> inactive: Condition Cleared\n& Below Threshold {
  class: transition
}

firing -> resolved: Alert Acknowledged\n& Condition Fixed {
  class: transition
}

resolved -> inactive: Reset Timer\n& Return to Monitoring {
  class: transition
}

firing -> firing: Condition Continues\n& Re-notification {
  class: transition
}

actions: |md
  **State Actions:**
  • **Inactive**: Monitor metrics, no notifications
  • **Pending**: Start evaluation timer, log event
  • **Firing**: Send notifications, escalate if needed
  • **Resolved**: Log resolution, update dashboards
| {
  shape: page
  style.fill: "#16213e"
  style.stroke: "#3fb950"
  style.font-color: "#e6edf3"
  near: bottom-right
}